motivation
----------

this guide will help you on how to use samba on nixos.

excerpt of /etc/nixos/configuration.nix
---------------------------------------

     ...
     services.samba.enable = true;
     services.samba.securityType = "share";
     services.samba.extraConfig = 
       workgroup = WORKGROUP
       server string = smbnix
       netbios name = smbnix
       security = share 
       #use sendfile = yes
       #max protocol = smb2
     
       [rw-files]
         comment = Temporary rw files 
         path = /storage
         read only = no
         writable = yes
         public = yes
     ;
     ...

afterwards apply the changes made to configuration.nix
------------------------------------------------------

     nixos-rebuild switch

samba should startup afterwards

stopping/restarting the services
--------------------------------

     stop samba
     start samba
     restart samba

